/* Independence proof #3 — THE GRAND CAPSTONE, image B (the non-witness set).
 *
 * Faculties whose link closure does NOT pull the ~1 GiB witness spine: the XII engine
 * certificates, decision procedures, math/crypto/zk arenas, type theory, consensus,
 * the sovereign ISA, and the non-witnessing Harmony Invariants.
 * See indep_cap_a.iii for THE HOST LAW (SizeOfImage < 0x77000000) that forces the
 * one-image capstone into weight-balanced images + the III-built driver.  Faculty
 * indices are the one-image capstone's ORIGINAL numbering, so a red exit names the
 * same organ.  Compiled AND linked by iiis-2 alone (no gcc). */
module indep_cap_b

extern @abi(c-msvc-x64) fn xjn_selftest() -> u64 from "xii_joinability.iii"
